{"tid":713671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台仔真係好撚冇用　屌你老母","createTime":"2018-06-23T04:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T04:50:09.000Z","uid":176366,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f6de8edbea5e021113543bedbe952c4aa35c38","tid":713671,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"一有台港嘅事<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 乜柒都講到lol<br />\n<br />\n台灣新聞又講LOL SV俾支那狗硬轉SERVER又講LOL<br />\n<br />\n「拜託其他也一併併入媽的不想看到港仔 」「真的 打lol的港仔都該回中國服 」<br />\n<br />\n成撚日就話支那點點點　又話台灣俾大陸講到死死吓 <br />\n<br />\n又話大學生俾支那搶去大陸返工<br />\n<br />\n又話中資搞到好多小店冇得做<br />\n<br />\n又話人哋人車車送曬過嚟到台大<br />\n<br />\n成撚日喺到呻大陸　一有事　唔好話講句公道啲說話<br />\n<br />\n佢哋可以即刻就同你割席　香港？ＷＦＣ<br />\n<br />\n用口嚟抗共不如快撚啲死"},{"pid":"93c0c83a20a8034bd50c6f0bf600af9f29c3f0e2","tid":713671,"uid":26232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"其實LOL台服係叫台港澳<br />\n另外LOL都係大陸㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過打機就咪咁認真<br />\n人地水平低就算啦"},{"pid":"3dabef64382afcd781d9d6de5aaca8139cea43c5","tid":713671,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"巴打咁勇唔驚俾崇台X咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608658b822c7a4e9064f34ecce3c85fb3c0305d2","tid":713671,"uid":57541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"台灣只有狗沒有人 台灣垃圾賤種狗地方"},{"pid":"3ed3d5538fb7e519ae5f77f07656a9b799b26706","tid":713671,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"巴哈個啲FORUM就算撚數喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個到嘅言論代表到台仔既話<br />\n香討都代表到香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nptt都一撚樣 全民大學生 個門檻有撚分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmo